    Caracteristică specială Unelte pentru animale de companie, rezistente la încurcături, până la 50 de minute
    Tipul filtrului Spumă
    Recomandare de suprafață Podea dură, covor
    Sursă de alimentare Alimentat cu baterii

    Despre acest articol

    • Design rezistent la încurcături: Ridică mai mult păr și elimină mai puține încurcături, fie că este vorba de păr uman sau de păr de animale.
    • Curățare versatilă: Curățați diferite tipuri de podele sau suprafețe cu accesoriile incluse.
    • Golire ușoară a recipientului de praf: Goliți recipientul de praf într-un coș de gunoi cu un singur clic, ori de câte ori se umple.
    • Ușor: Ridicați cu ușurință aspiratorul ușor pentru o sesiune rapidă de curățare.
    • Filtre lavabile: Profitați la maximum de filtrele dumneavoastră spălându-le și reutilizându-le.
    • Rolă ușor de curățat: Rola este detașabilă și lavabilă.
    • Excelent pentru animale de companie și alergii: filtrarea în 5 etape captează și reține eficient părul și mătreața animalelor.*
    • Up to 50-Min Runtime
    • Tangle-Resistant Roller
    • 2-in-1 Crevice Tool
    • 2-in-1 Pet Tool
    • 5-Stage Filtration
    • Lightweight

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

      • Savannahnan
        5.0 out of 5 stars We really like this vacuum; it has been a real game-changer for us! Highly recommended!!!
        Reviewed in the United States on February 24, 2026
        Style: LVAC-200 EssentialVerified Purchase
        We bought this model of Levoit vacuum (the LVAC-200) after using the more expensive model at work (the LVAC-300). The 300 was so terrific to use at work that we wanted to get a Levoit for our home. However, we didn't need the larger size dust collector canister that the 300 has (which is perfect for doing a huge amount of carpeting in a professional building), so we went with the more economical 200 model.

        The model 200 has been excellent for home use. The vacuum is super easy to set up and use. The suction power is very good. The battery charge lasts at least 45 minutes of continual use. The tangle resistant roller design is important, since we have two long haired spaniels. In fact, I haven't had the need to pull hair out of the rollers like I always had to do with our Eureka WindTunnel. The dust collector is easy to clean. The vacuum is very light and easy to maneuver. The brush head can turn into a 90" angle when vacuuming, so it can get way into corners and small spaces. You can fold it completely flat to vacuum way under the beds.

        We have compared using this vacuum to our Eureka WindTunnel by thoroughly vacuuming a carpet first with the WindTunnel. Then, we vacuumed the same carpet with the Levoit. The Levoit picked up a ton of dirt and hair that the WindTunnel missed. It was pretty shocking how much the WindTunnel missed.

        I also love the fact that we don't have to adjust the roller height for different surfaces (like we always had to do with the WindTunnel). The Levoit moves effortlessly from bare floor to carpeting and doesn't miss any of the dirt along the edges of the carpet. When you look closely at the bare floor after vacuuming, you can see that the Levoit really got all the dust off the surface. Great suction power.

        We did go ahead and purchase additional batteries so we can always have one charging and ready to go. We also got extra filters.

        The Levoit customer service is very responsive, friendly, and professional. We had a question which they answered within 24 hours and then they followed up again to make sure that they completely answered our question (they did) and to see if we needed any further assistance. Very cool.

        I guess you can see that we really like this vacuum; it has been a real game-changer for us. I actually look forward to vacuuming.

        2do punto ⚫️ duré cinco años con mi aspiradora anterior, era una aspiradora común, como dicen, ni muy muy ni tan tan, pero sinceramente era una maravilla, aguantó tanta carrilla y la amaba porque además la compré a un bajo costo ( aquí mismo en Amazon) y lo que más me gustaba es que era muy ligera, si lo que quieres es algo ligero con esta aspiradora no lo obtendrás, me considero muy débil porque no hago nada de ejercicio y no me alimento bien y la aspiradora se me hace extremadamente pesada, mi casa no es una mansión, pero aún así con dos recámaras, sala, cocina, me deja el brazo, todo cansado, en realidad a mí en lo personal me parece muy muy pesada, así que contemplen eso que van a tener que ponerse en modo fuertes para poder maniobrarla ya que ligera no es 🥲.

        3er punto ⚫️ hace un ruido que parece que encendiste un tractor. Ja ja ja, yo acostumbro a hacer el aseo muy temprano por la mañana, digamos entre 6, 7 de la mañana y como vivo en condominios, hoy me da vergüenza encenderla porque es un ruido que obviamente se va a escuchar y despertar a mis vecinos, sinceramente no entiendo cómo habiendo tanta tecnología no la hicieron de una manera un poquito mas silenciosa caray, incluso a mí me molesta tanto el ruido que me tengo que poner mis AirPods mientras aspiro porque no soporto el ruido.

        4to punto ⚫️ la base del área que aspira es bastante tosca y ancha. Entonces en las superficies y áreas que yo acostumbrada meter mi aspiradora anterior para limpiar, Ahora ya no puedo, por ejemplo, en el área de debajo del refrigerador o de mi sofá, simplemente es imposible porque no me fijé al comprarla o mejor dicho no me imaginé que fuera a hacer tan ancha, esto lo digo con mucho dolor porque extraño tanto mi aspiradora anterior tan ligera y que cabía en todos lados 🥲

        ✅ puntos a favor:
        🟢 la aspiradora, pues es bonita y se ve moderna.
        🟢 es muy fácil, retirar el filtro para sacar la basura que aspiraste.
        🟢 la carga, no me puedo quejar, si le dura demasiado.

        Pd. Siempre extrañaré a mi gran aspiradora barata que me duró cinco años y fue mi gran compañera de limpieza, les pido un minuto de silencio por ella.😌
